1 - clean install the games
2 - download MLMO2 to /home
3 - download xNVSE
4 - extract xNVSE to the game folder
5 - add MLMO2 to Steam as a non-Steam game
6 - create prefix for MLMO2
7 - use Protontricks to install dependencies onto MLMO2 prefix
8 - launch MLMO2 from Steam
9 - guide user through first time setup of MLMO2
10 - download VNV/TBOT mods automatically using hoolamike
11 - if TTW install TTW with Hoolamike
12 - if not 4GB patch New Vegas with Hoolamike
13 - done
